Task1 : Create User :
sudo useradd -m username : This command create user with directory
-m creates folder for that user
eg. sudo useradd -m saroj

sudo passwd username
eg. sudo passwd saroj
     New Password :srk12345

Task 2: Switch user
 su username
eg. su saroj

Task3: Verify home directory
ls /home
ls -ld/home/saroj
